---
import Install from './Install';
---
<section id="install" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-text">
      One line. <span class="italic font-medium text-brand">You're done.</span>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <Install client:visible />
  <p class="mt-5 text-xs text-text-subtle">
    macOS: TOFA isn't notarized yet, so macOS quarantines it on first launch.
    See the <a class="text-brand underline underline-offset-2" href="https://docs.tofa.stratif.io/security.html#unsigned-build">unsigned-build note</a> for the one-line fix.
  </p>
</section>
